WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 21=

00:01:40.650 --> 00:01:41.700 line:80%
I've told Lingbo.

00:01:42.030 --> 00:01:43.370 line:80%
I'll call off the engagement
when back.

00:01:49.650 --> 00:01:50.490 line:80%
That's so sudden.

00:01:51.140 --> 00:01:52.060 line:80%
Lingbo, she...

00:01:52.090 --> 00:01:53.010 line:80%
It's not her fault.

00:01:54.340 --> 00:01:55.540 line:80%
Just mine.

00:01:57.780 --> 00:01:58.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:02.090 --> 00:02:02.930 line:80%
I...

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:05.570 line:80%
I'm drunk and free with the breeze.

00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:06.780 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:02:08.780 --> 00:02:09.690 line:80%
What are you up to?

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:12.210 line:80%
Isn't the sacrificial rite in two days?

00:02:12.210 --> 00:02:13.460 line:80%
I'm preparing some offerings.

00:02:13.460 --> 00:02:15.460 line:80%
Three vegetarian fruits
and three vegetarian pastries.

00:02:15.460 --> 00:02:16.300 line:80%
Six varieties in total.

00:02:17.250 --> 00:02:18.120 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:19.090 line:80%
The cemetery is cold.

00:02:19.090 --> 00:02:20.340 line:80%
Remember to wear more.

00:02:27.860 --> 00:02:33.420 line:80%
(Chang Cemetery)

00:02:36.810 --> 00:02:37.650 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:39.300 --> 00:02:41.580 line:80%
Zhao, you also think the Jade Sunflower

00:02:41.580 --> 00:02:43.340 line:80%
is hidden within the Chang Cemetery?

00:02:44.580 --> 00:02:45.460 line:80%
You and I

00:02:46.060 --> 00:02:47.530 line:80%
truly share the same thoughts.

00:02:48.650 --> 00:02:49.490 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:51.690 --> 00:02:53.340 line:80%
Yuzhi, why are you here too?

00:02:53.780 --> 00:02:54.620 line:80%
I told you

00:02:55.090 --> 00:02:56.490 line:80%
I'd look out for you from now on.

00:02:58.900 --> 00:03:00.210 line:80%
Zhao has me. That's enough.

00:03:01.210 --> 00:03:02.860 line:80%
No need for Song to trouble yourself.

00:03:05.530 --> 00:03:07.180 line:80%
The letter I sent you,

00:03:07.180 --> 00:03:08.180 line:80%
you showed it to him as well?

00:03:08.780 --> 00:03:10.210 line:80%
Zhao is here to help me

00:03:10.210 --> 00:03:11.580 line:80%
find the Jade Sunflower.

00:03:12.410 --> 00:03:13.740 line:80%
May I ask why

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:15.300 line:80%
Mr. Mu is here?

00:03:15.490 --> 00:03:16.970 line:80%
Where Zhao goes, I go.

00:03:18.210 --> 00:03:19.210 line:80%
What Zhao does,

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:21.140 line:80%
I do.

00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:22.930 line:80%
Both of you, leave now.

00:03:36.140 --> 00:03:37.490 line:80%
Since you're done arguing,

00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:40.090 line:80%
stay and talk sense.

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:42.370 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:03:42.370 --> 00:03:43.620 line:80%
why did you suspect

00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:44.650 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower

00:03:44.650 --> 00:03:46.090 line:80%
was hidden in the Chang Cemetery?

00:03:46.090 --> 00:03:47.460 line:80%
Nie Zhe's men

00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:49.900 line:80%
searched every corner of the Chang Fort,

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:51.620 line:80%
yet they didn't find it.

00:03:51.620 --> 00:03:53.020 line:80%
After thinking it over,

00:03:53.020 --> 00:03:54.300 line:80%
it seemed only the cemetery

00:03:54.300 --> 00:03:56.300 line:80%
was the one place
they might have overlooked.

00:03:56.300 --> 00:03:58.300 line:80%
So I got some brothers
who're good at digging graves.

00:03:59.620 --> 00:04:01.650 line:80%
Mr. Mu's brilliant idea

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:02.690 line:80%
is to dig up graves?

00:04:02.690 --> 00:04:04.180 line:80%
If we don't dig,

00:04:04.180 --> 00:04:06.140 line:80%
does Song have a better plan?

00:04:06.650 --> 00:04:07.650 line:80%
Enough.

00:04:10.530 --> 00:04:11.740 line:80%
Over a decade ago,

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:13.180 line:80%
my Dad brought me here.

00:04:18.900 --> 00:04:19.740 line:80%
You two

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:21.020 line:80%
joined Chang in ancestor worship.

00:04:21.020 --> 00:04:22.140 line:80%
How did you both get sunburned?

00:04:22.530 --> 00:04:23.650 line:80%
But I've been here twice

00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:25.940 line:80%
and didn't find any

00:04:25.940 --> 00:04:27.140 line:80%
sunny spots.

00:04:42.140 --> 00:04:43.780 line:80%
Could the problem be
with this stone pillar?

00:04:44.340 --> 00:04:45.530 line:80%
Then let's just topple it.

00:04:45.530 --> 00:04:46.370 line:80%
I'll call someone now.

00:04:48.090 --> 00:04:49.050 line:80%
Wait.

00:04:53.290 --> 00:04:54.130 line:80%
Don't call anyone yet.

00:04:54.650 --> 00:04:56.140 line:80%
Does Zhao want to stay here

00:04:56.580 --> 00:04:58.900 line:80%
searching with me forever?

00:04:59.410 --> 00:05:00.340 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:05:01.170 --> 00:05:02.290 line:80%
please mind your manners.

00:05:09.430 --> 00:05:10.420 line:80%
Let's get down to business.

00:05:11.090 --> 00:05:13.970 line:80%
So the mirror surface
is what gave me sunburn.

00:05:13.970 --> 00:05:15.020 line:80%
The back mountain is shaded.

00:05:15.020 --> 00:05:16.210 line:80%
Sunlight's scarce.

00:05:16.210 --> 00:05:17.700 line:80%
Logically,

00:05:17.700 --> 00:05:20.090 line:80%
it shouldn't burn anyone.

00:05:21.700 --> 00:05:23.290 line:80%
But with this bronze mirror,

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:25.090 line:80%
the faint sunlight

00:05:25.090 --> 00:05:26.580 line:80%
can be concentrated several times

00:05:26.580 --> 00:05:27.820 line:80%
and reflected to the other side.

00:05:29.050 --> 00:05:30.850 line:80%
But the stone pillar sank down.

00:05:30.850 --> 00:05:32.700 line:80%
So both times,

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:34.090 line:80%
I avoided being burned.

00:05:34.780 --> 00:05:37.340 line:80%
Wu'an Mountain is made of hard granite,

00:05:37.820 --> 00:05:38.940 line:80%
with dense forests.

00:05:39.500 --> 00:05:41.290 line:80%
Its foundation should be firm.

00:05:41.700 --> 00:05:44.140 line:80%
It can't just sink for no reason.

00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:45.700 line:80%
Unless...

00:05:45.700 --> 00:05:46.730 line:80%
The ground below was hollowed.

00:05:47.820 --> 00:05:49.410 line:80%
Do you remember

00:05:49.410 --> 00:05:51.020 line:80%
the Shi brothers,
my aunt's good friends?

00:05:51.020 --> 00:05:53.090 line:80%
The second Shi brother
was struck by Nether Aura.

00:05:53.580 --> 00:05:54.900 line:80%
But your aunt cured him later.

00:05:55.410 --> 00:05:56.460 line:80%
That's why

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:58.050 line:80%
you're looking for
the Jade Sunflower for him.

00:06:02.730 --> 00:06:03.970 line:80%
Are the Shi brothers

00:06:04.530 --> 00:06:05.780 line:80%
tomb raiders by trade?

00:06:09.340 --> 00:06:10.290 line:80%
The Shi brothers

00:06:10.290 --> 00:06:12.460 line:80%
gave my aunt
some family heirlooms before.

00:06:12.460 --> 00:06:14.970 line:80%
As a child, I'd flip through them
out of boredom.

00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:17.170 line:80%
Inside, it was all records of

00:06:17.170 --> 00:06:19.940 line:80%
the skills and methods
for building subterranean tombs.

00:06:19.940 --> 00:06:22.900 line:80%
Don't think constructing
a subterranean tomb is easy.

00:06:22.900 --> 00:06:24.170 line:80%
You must guard against water seepage.

00:06:24.170 --> 00:06:26.050 line:80%
And against rats, insects,
snakes, and ants.

00:06:26.050 --> 00:06:27.140 line:80%
After sealing the entrance,

00:06:27.140 --> 00:06:28.780 line:80%
you must leave no trace behind.

00:06:28.780 --> 00:06:30.090 line:80%
There are so many tricks to it.

00:06:38.580 --> 00:06:39.970 line:80%
South is Li. North is Kan.

00:06:40.530 --> 00:06:41.970 line:80%
Kan is one. Qian is six.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.650 line:80%
Kun, in the southwest, commands the yin.

00:06:44.460 --> 00:06:46.850 line:80%
Align with the cycles of life and death.

00:06:48.090 --> 00:06:49.140 line:80%
The entrance is right here.

00:06:49.140 --> 00:06:49.980 line:80%
- Alright.
- Alright.

00:06:49.990 --> 00:06:51.110 line:80%
- Miss Cai decides.
- Zhao leads.

00:07:27.140 --> 00:07:28.340 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:07:28.340 --> 00:07:30.610 line:80%
Does this wall have

00:07:31.700 --> 00:07:32.700 line:80%
any meaning in tomb lore?

00:07:33.090 --> 00:07:34.050 line:80%
It's the Turnback Wall.

00:07:34.430 --> 00:07:35.900 line:80%
A signature skill of the Shi brothers.

00:07:36.700 --> 00:07:38.050 line:80%
The mechanism should be nearby.

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:54.290 line:80%
Do we need a key?

00:08:01.900 --> 00:08:02.970 line:80%
You actually have one?

00:08:07.460 --> 00:08:08.300 line:80%
There's no keyhole.

00:08:10.410 --> 00:08:11.250 line:80%
Lock latch?

00:08:22.580 --> 00:08:23.650 line:80%
Where'd that come from?

00:08:23.650 --> 00:08:25.050 line:80%
Mr. Chang left it to me.

00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:26.530 line:80%
Back then, Jiang Ning changed his tone.

00:08:26.970 --> 00:08:28.210 line:80%
Only after seeing this.

00:08:28.580 --> 00:08:30.380 line:80%
Uncle Chang truly trusts you.

00:08:58.570 --> 00:08:59.500 line:80%
Light the lamps first.

00:09:10.580 --> 00:09:12.860 line:80%
(Memorial tablet of Lu Chengnan
from the Li Sect)

00:09:13.380 --> 00:09:14.930 line:80%
Lu Chengnan is really dead.

00:09:16.330 --> 00:09:18.020 line:80%
This looks like my aunt's handwriting.

00:09:21.930 --> 00:09:23.050 line:80%
Sun rises. Moon sets.

00:09:23.690 --> 00:09:25.620 line:80%
You've always walked alone.

00:09:25.620 --> 00:09:27.330 line:80%
Both bold and noble.

00:09:27.330 --> 00:09:29.500 line:80%
Lofty mountains and flowing rivers.

00:09:29.500 --> 00:09:31.530 line:80%
Lord, as you depart.

00:09:31.530 --> 00:09:33.220 line:80%
May your journey be free of obstacles.

00:09:41.100 --> 00:09:43.410 line:80%
This tomb was built by the Shi brothers.

00:09:43.410 --> 00:09:45.050 line:80%
It bears my aunt's own handwriting.

00:09:45.810 --> 00:09:47.380 line:80%
Could Lu Chengnan

00:09:47.380 --> 00:09:48.570 line:80%
really be a skin-painted demon?

00:09:49.170 --> 00:09:51.380 line:80%
Though he was from the Li Sect,

00:09:51.380 --> 00:09:52.930 line:80%
he received such honor.

00:09:52.930 --> 00:09:53.860 line:80%
Could

00:09:53.860 --> 00:09:55.100 line:80%
he have been a righteous man?

00:09:55.100 --> 00:09:55.980 line:80%
Let's find

00:09:56.500 --> 00:09:57.450 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower first.

00:10:13.410 --> 00:10:14.330 line:80%
Could it be

00:10:14.810 --> 00:10:16.140 line:80%
in this stone coffin?

00:10:18.900 --> 00:10:19.740 line:80%
Wait.

00:10:21.050 --> 00:10:21.890 line:80%
Elder.

00:10:22.380 --> 00:10:23.220 line:80%
Sorry to interrupt.

00:10:27.620 --> 00:10:28.570 line:80%
Not inside.

00:10:31.860 --> 00:10:32.980 line:80%
Sternum shattered,

00:10:33.500 --> 00:10:35.170 line:80%
surrounding bones cracked.

00:10:35.170 --> 00:10:36.860 line:80%
Even the underarm ribs are broken.

00:10:36.860 --> 00:10:38.100 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng's signature move.

00:10:38.810 --> 00:10:40.290 line:80%
Soulreaving Cloud Palm.

00:10:40.290 --> 00:10:41.930 line:80%
Elder Yan's words were all true.

00:10:41.930 --> 00:10:44.100 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng really killed Lu Chengnan.

00:10:44.740 --> 00:10:46.290 line:80%
What's so mysterious

00:10:46.290 --> 00:10:47.900 line:80%
about the Jade Sunflower?

00:10:47.900 --> 00:10:48.810 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng

00:10:48.810 --> 00:10:51.170 line:80%
killed his favorite disciple for it.

00:10:51.170 --> 00:10:52.740 line:80%
Nie Zhe and the Man in Black

00:10:52.740 --> 00:10:53.860 line:80%
massacred

00:10:53.860 --> 00:10:55.810 line:80%
Uncle Chang's entire family for it.

00:10:55.810 --> 00:10:57.330 line:80%
Once we find the Jade Sunflower,

00:10:57.330 --> 00:10:58.500 line:80%
everything will be clear.

00:10:59.020 --> 00:10:59.980 line:80%
Maybe

00:11:00.860 --> 00:11:02.810 line:80%
we can ask the tomb builders.

00:11:02.810 --> 00:11:04.690 line:80%
But the Shi brothers have retired.

00:11:04.690 --> 00:11:05.810 line:80%
My Master and Father

00:11:05.810 --> 00:11:07.740 line:80%
don't even know

00:11:07.740 --> 00:11:08.860 line:80%
where they are.

00:11:10.780 --> 00:11:12.050 line:80%
Let's get out first and talk.

00:11:17.620 --> 00:11:18.530 line:80%
Don't move.

00:11:19.220 --> 00:11:20.100 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:11:20.100 --> 00:11:21.650 line:80%
they all die.

00:11:36.690 --> 00:11:37.530 line:80%
Nie Zhe.

00:11:37.860 --> 00:11:39.500 line:80%
If you dare harm them,

00:11:39.500 --> 00:11:41.410 line:80%
the Six Sects will hunt you down

00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:42.690 line:80%
to the last person!

00:11:43.290 --> 00:11:44.140 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:11:44.140 --> 00:11:45.410 line:80%
We didn't come to

00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:47.620 line:80%
be enemies with the Six Sects.

00:11:47.930 --> 00:11:49.740 line:80%
Just hand over the Jade Sunflower,

00:11:49.740 --> 00:11:51.690 line:80%
and we'll let them go.

00:11:52.050 --> 00:11:53.650 line:80%
What do you think, Mr. Mu?

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.450 line:80%
You seized people from the Six Sects.

00:11:56.220 --> 00:11:57.620 line:80%
What has that to do with me?

00:11:58.810 --> 00:12:01.500 line:80%
They're all kin
to the leaders of the Six Sects.

00:12:02.050 --> 00:12:03.570 line:80%
If they die,

00:12:03.570 --> 00:12:05.380 line:80%
Six Sects and Li Sect are going to war.

00:12:05.380 --> 00:12:06.620 line:80%
By then,

00:12:06.620 --> 00:12:08.290 line:80%
can you still hold onto

00:12:09.140 --> 00:12:10.740 line:80%
your position as Young Master?

00:12:11.100 --> 00:12:12.140 line:80%
So what?

00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:15.140 line:80%
Fine, fine.

00:12:17.410 --> 00:12:18.250 line:80%
Wait!

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:23.940 line:80%
Hand it over.

00:12:27.860 --> 00:12:28.700 line:80%
Hand it over!

00:12:42.290 --> 00:12:43.170 line:80%
Here, take it.

00:12:53.170 --> 00:12:54.020 line:80%
Strategist!

00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:56.570 line:80%
My face! My face!

00:12:56.570 --> 00:12:57.930 line:80%
Someone! Hurry!

00:13:06.230 --> 00:13:07.380 line:80%
Get the strategist out first!

00:13:07.380 --> 00:13:08.220 line:80%
Hurry!

00:13:51.230 --> 00:13:52.860 line:80%
The softening powder's effects
are gone now.

00:13:52.860 --> 00:13:54.170 line:80%
Stay hydrated for the next two days.

00:13:54.170 --> 00:13:55.010 line:80%
I won't drink!

00:14:05.530 --> 00:14:07.100 line:80%
Teaming up with Mu Qingyan this time

00:14:07.100 --> 00:14:08.650 line:80%
was indeed my own decision.

00:14:09.220 --> 00:14:10.980 line:80%
But Nie Zhe is lurking nearby,

00:14:10.980 --> 00:14:12.410 line:80%
and if we don't draw him out now,

00:14:12.410 --> 00:14:13.740 line:80%
no one knows when he'll surface again.

00:14:14.650 --> 00:14:15.980 line:80%
That softening powder everyone got.

00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:18.020 line:80%
Master You tested its effects
beforehand.

00:14:18.020 --> 00:14:19.570 line:80%
I kept this from everyone,

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:21.740 line:80%
because Nie Zhe's spies
are near the inn.

00:14:21.740 --> 00:14:23.220 line:80%
You could have hidden it from us,

00:14:23.220 --> 00:14:24.620 line:80%
so why tell Cai Zhao?

00:14:25.170 --> 00:14:26.290 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:14:26.290 --> 00:14:28.220 line:80%
I only found out

00:14:28.220 --> 00:14:29.620 line:80%
right before you arrived.

00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:31.650 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:14:31.650 --> 00:14:33.650 line:80%
when did you arrange this
with Mu Qingyan?

00:14:35.100 --> 00:14:37.980 line:80%
Since Nie Zhe is so fixated on
the Jade Sunflower,

00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:39.650 line:80%
why not use this chance to lure him out?

00:14:40.290 --> 00:14:42.380 line:80%
I'm sure you feel the same.

00:14:42.380 --> 00:14:43.690 line:80%
Nie Zhe is cunning and suspicious.

00:14:44.420 --> 00:14:45.860 line:80%
If we want to force him to show himself,

00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:49.290 line:80%
we'll need to offer him
something tempting.

00:14:52.860 --> 00:14:54.380 line:80%
Didn't expect you two guys

00:14:54.380 --> 00:14:55.740 line:80%
have little secrets.

00:14:56.980 --> 00:14:57.930 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:14:57.930 --> 00:14:59.930 line:80%
It's bad enough
you're tangled up with Mu Qingyan.

00:15:00.380 --> 00:15:01.740 line:80%
Why must you drag Yuzhi into this too?

00:15:02.020 --> 00:15:03.220 line:80%
Me and Mu Qingyan.

00:15:03.810 --> 00:15:05.050 line:80%
How exactly are we tangled up?

00:15:05.050 --> 00:15:07.570 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou isn't here right now,
drop the act.

00:15:08.220 --> 00:15:10.330 line:80%
You clearly like Mu Qingyan.

00:15:10.520 --> 00:15:12.690 line:80%
You two were close
back when you were in Qingque Sect.

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:15.020 line:80%
So why would he have followed you
all the way to the inn?

00:15:15.740 --> 00:15:16.580 line:80%
Speaking of which,

00:15:17.320 --> 00:15:18.450 line:80%
someone from your Luoying Valley

00:15:18.450 --> 00:15:20.780 line:80%
fraternized with the demon sect before.

00:15:21.220 --> 00:15:22.410 line:80%
Some habits just never change!

00:15:24.170 --> 00:15:25.900 line:80%
Insult me all you want.

00:15:25.900 --> 00:15:27.570 line:80%
But don't you dare
insult Luoying Valley.

00:15:27.570 --> 00:15:28.860 line:80%
I'll say it!

00:15:28.860 --> 00:15:29.930 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:15:29.930 --> 00:15:31.740 line:80%
Nie Zhe is the murderer
of the Chang clan.

00:15:31.740 --> 00:15:32.860 line:80%
Teaming up with Mu Qingyan

00:15:32.860 --> 00:15:34.170 line:80%
to catch him was a necessary compromise.

00:15:34.170 --> 00:15:36.290 line:80%
Besides, the idea of cooperation
came from me.

00:15:36.290 --> 00:15:37.220 line:80%
Zhao's out of it.

00:15:39.620 --> 00:15:40.570 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:44.220 line:80%
Young Master requests your presence.

00:15:45.780 --> 00:15:46.620 line:80%
Alright.

00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:48.810 line:80%
No more hiding.

00:15:48.810 --> 00:15:49.650 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:15:50.220 --> 00:15:51.380 line:80%
Don't forget

00:15:51.780 --> 00:15:53.530 line:80%
you have a fiancé.

00:15:56.100 --> 00:15:56.940 line:80%
Why does he want me?

00:15:57.140 --> 00:15:58.100 line:80%
Elder Hu has confessed.

00:15:58.100 --> 00:16:00.140 line:80%
He also asks Mr. Song to come.

00:16:00.140 --> 00:16:01.220 line:80%
You Guanyue.

00:16:01.780 --> 00:16:03.740 line:80%
Can't you say it all at once?

00:16:03.740 --> 00:16:04.590 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:05.900 line:80%
The Young Master asks you to come.

00:16:05.900 --> 00:16:06.810 line:80%
Elder Hu has confessed.

00:16:06.810 --> 00:16:09.220 line:80%
Mr. Song is also invited.

00:16:17.140 --> 00:16:19.780 line:80%
The mastermind you've been looking for

00:16:21.620 --> 00:16:23.330 line:80%
is one of the Six Sects.

00:16:23.930 --> 00:16:24.770 line:80%
Elder Hu.

00:16:26.100 --> 00:16:28.170 line:80%
That mysterious man
moved freely in the Li Sect.

00:16:28.170 --> 00:16:29.620 line:80%
He's clearly one of the Li Sect.

00:16:29.620 --> 00:16:31.330 line:80%
Why spout nonsense

00:16:31.330 --> 00:16:32.290 line:80%
and stir up trouble?

00:16:32.780 --> 00:16:34.140 line:80%
Believe it or not, it's up to you.

00:16:34.740 --> 00:16:36.170 line:80%
But you Six Sects

00:16:36.900 --> 00:16:37.930 line:80%
have done plenty of

00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:39.690 line:80%
self-deceptive things.

00:16:40.220 --> 00:16:41.060 line:80%
You...

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:53.930 line:80%
Do you also think
it's one of the Six Sects?

00:16:53.930 --> 00:16:55.170 line:80%
Earlier, the Six Sects were attacked,

00:16:56.220 --> 00:16:57.780 line:80%
the mysterious man leaked

00:16:57.780 --> 00:16:59.620 line:80%
everyone's whereabouts to Nie Zhe.

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:01.170 line:80%
Such confidential information.

00:17:01.170 --> 00:17:02.500 line:80%
Besides the Six Sects' leaders,

00:17:02.500 --> 00:17:03.900 line:80%
who else would know?

00:17:03.900 --> 00:17:04.780 line:80%
Besides,

00:17:04.780 --> 00:17:06.500 line:80%
I fought the Man in Black twice.

00:17:07.050 --> 00:17:08.180 line:80%
His skill

00:17:08.180 --> 00:17:09.370 line:80%
is unfathomable,

00:17:09.370 --> 00:17:10.810 line:80%
no ordinary fighter.

00:17:11.460 --> 00:17:12.570 line:80%
I think he's at

00:17:13.710 --> 00:17:14.650 line:80%
Grandmaster level.

00:17:14.660 --> 00:17:16.160 line:80%
Grandmaster level.

00:17:17.130 --> 00:17:19.050 line:80%
Only the Six Sects' leaders

00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:20.460 line:80%
reach this rank.

00:17:21.290 --> 00:17:22.130 line:80%
My Master

00:17:22.270 --> 00:17:23.700 line:80%
is already the Lord of the Six Sects.

00:17:24.130 --> 00:17:25.530 line:80%
Why would he ally with Nie Zhe?

00:17:26.850 --> 00:17:28.130 line:80%
Uncle Zhou's detached from fame,

00:17:28.130 --> 00:17:29.460 line:80%
devoted to crafting weapons.

00:17:29.460 --> 00:17:30.570 line:80%
No motive for this.

00:17:31.220 --> 00:17:33.020 line:80%
The Taichu Temple
just changed leadership.

00:17:33.330 --> 00:17:35.130 line:80%
As for Yang Heying of the Siqi Sect,

00:17:35.130 --> 00:17:36.220 line:80%
he can't even beat me.

00:17:38.290 --> 00:17:39.180 line:80%
And Lord Song.

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:41.220 line:80%
While it's plausible

00:17:41.220 --> 00:17:42.890 line:80%
my father'd vie for
Lord of the Six Sects,

00:17:42.890 --> 00:17:44.220 line:80%
colluding with the demon sect

00:17:44.220 --> 00:17:45.420 line:80%
for ulterior motives?

00:17:45.420 --> 00:17:46.780 line:80%
That's absolutely impossible.

00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:49.050 line:80%
Exactly. Lord Song's pragmatic.

00:17:49.050 --> 00:17:50.940 line:80%
For gains he can't see or touch,

00:17:50.940 --> 00:17:52.180 line:80%
he wouldn't waste a single effort.

00:17:52.180 --> 00:17:53.020 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:17:54.370 --> 00:17:56.220 line:80%
you're not suspecting Mr. Cai, are you?

00:17:56.740 --> 00:17:57.780 line:80%
Who the Man in Black is?

00:17:58.420 --> 00:17:59.530 line:80%
Once we capture Nie Zhe alive,

00:17:59.850 --> 00:18:00.780 line:80%
we'll know.

00:18:01.220 --> 00:18:02.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:18:02.530 --> 00:18:04.090 line:80%
as long as we find the Jade Sunflower,

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:05.570 line:80%
he'll show himself.

00:18:06.180 --> 00:18:08.530 line:80%
The Six Sects' leaders
can't be traitors.

00:18:08.530 --> 00:18:09.940 line:80%
Even if secrets were leaked,

00:18:09.940 --> 00:18:11.980 line:80%
it would only mean
Nie Zhe has a spy in the sects.

00:18:13.370 --> 00:18:14.210 line:80%
Zhao.

00:18:14.420 --> 00:18:15.260 line:80%
This is critical.

00:18:15.700 --> 00:18:17.290 line:80%
We must return to the sect at once.

00:18:17.290 --> 00:18:18.130 line:80%
And report to Master.

00:18:20.460 --> 00:18:21.890 line:80%
Once we've honored Mr. Chang tomorrow,

00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:23.700 line:80%
we'll set out back home.

00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:35.570 line:80%
Zhao also thinks

00:18:35.980 --> 00:18:37.530 line:80%
the mastermind is from the Six Sects?

00:18:39.700 --> 00:18:41.810 line:80%
Not Master or the others, but...

00:18:41.810 --> 00:18:43.420 line:80%
But you still have doubts.

00:18:43.990 --> 00:18:45.780 line:80%
You think it might be
someone from the sects.

00:18:46.370 --> 00:18:47.700 line:80%
Wasn't Mr. Wu

00:18:47.700 --> 00:18:49.530 line:80%
killed by Qiu Yuanfeng?

00:18:49.530 --> 00:18:50.460 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng

00:18:50.460 --> 00:18:51.740 line:80%
was a former sect leader.

00:18:52.500 --> 00:18:54.500 line:80%
Sometimes good and evil
hinge on a single thought.

00:18:54.940 --> 00:18:56.660 line:80%
Whatever that figure is plotting,

00:18:57.610 --> 00:18:59.180 line:80%
it's mostly

00:18:59.180 --> 00:19:00.370 line:80%
tied to the Six Sects.

00:19:00.370 --> 00:19:02.050 line:80%
Mr. Wu's case was an accident.

00:19:02.050 --> 00:19:03.420 line:80%
Good and evil may be a thought apart,

00:19:03.980 --> 00:19:05.370 line:80%
but the mastermind has planned

00:19:05.370 --> 00:19:06.290 line:80%
for over ten years.

00:19:06.560 --> 00:19:08.050 line:80%
This isn't a spur-of-the-moment thing.

00:19:08.050 --> 00:19:08.890 line:80%
Besides,

00:19:09.610 --> 00:19:11.700 line:80%
Hu Fengge is a demon sect elder.

00:19:11.700 --> 00:19:13.780 line:80%
How credible is her testimony?

00:19:13.780 --> 00:19:15.370 line:80%
Maybe her capture was a deliberate

00:19:15.890 --> 00:19:16.940 line:80%
divide-and-conquer tactic.

00:19:17.220 --> 00:19:18.780 line:80%
Since the key is the Jade Sunflower,

00:19:19.700 --> 00:19:21.180 line:80%
then let's find it.

00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:24.290 line:80%
Maybe then the truth will come to light.

00:19:24.290 --> 00:19:25.180 line:80%
Besides, Yuzhi,

00:19:25.180 --> 00:19:26.660 line:80%
you need it to dispel the cold.

00:19:26.660 --> 00:19:28.020 line:80%
I can do without the Jade Sunflower.

00:19:28.460 --> 00:19:30.050 line:80%
I'll just train harder from now on.

00:19:30.570 --> 00:19:31.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:32.370 --> 00:19:34.330 line:80%
Mu Qingyan's identity
is common knowledge.

00:19:34.330 --> 00:19:35.890 line:80%
No one can cover for us this time.

00:19:37.570 --> 00:19:38.570 line:80%
Once we take this step,

00:19:39.940 --> 00:19:41.050 line:80%
there's no turning back.

00:19:42.530 --> 00:19:43.370 line:80%
I know.

00:19:43.500 --> 00:19:44.460 line:80%
I'm at fault this time.

00:19:45.220 --> 00:19:46.780 line:80%
I was too eager to
catch ringleader Nie Zhe,

00:19:46.780 --> 00:19:48.530 line:80%
so I chose to work with Mu Qingyan.

00:19:48.530 --> 00:19:50.050 line:80%
I not only put us in disrepute,

00:19:50.050 --> 00:19:51.530 line:80%
but also endangered
Lingbo and the others.

00:19:52.090 --> 00:19:53.610 line:80%
Don't mind

00:19:54.850 --> 00:19:55.810 line:80%
what Lingbo said earlier.

00:19:56.940 --> 00:19:58.020 line:80%
She's mad at me.

00:20:16.940 --> 00:20:17.780 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:20:18.890 --> 00:20:20.020 line:80%
Why are you here alone?

00:20:24.660 --> 00:20:25.570 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:20:25.570 --> 00:20:26.410 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

00:20:30.020 --> 00:20:31.740 line:80%
Yuzhi was reckless this time.

00:20:32.460 --> 00:20:33.530 line:80%
But I don't think

00:20:33.530 --> 00:20:34.850 line:80%
Cai Zhao knew about it.

00:20:40.520 --> 00:20:41.610 line:80%
He's calling off the engagement.

00:20:41.940 --> 00:20:43.180 line:80%
Yuzhi's calling off the engagement?

00:20:43.610 --> 00:20:44.450 line:80%
When?

00:20:44.700 --> 00:20:45.660 line:80%
Yesterday.

00:20:46.460 --> 00:20:47.570 line:80%
When we went to find him.

00:20:50.130 --> 00:20:51.090 line:80%
Yuzhi, he...

00:20:54.850 --> 00:20:55.690 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:20:56.500 --> 00:20:57.340 line:80%
What

00:20:57.780 --> 00:20:59.370 line:80%
do you truly think?

00:20:59.370 --> 00:21:00.330 line:80%
I don't know.

00:21:02.940 --> 00:21:05.500 line:80%
I grew up thinking
I'd marry Yuzhi.

00:21:06.090 --> 00:21:07.420 line:80%
Now the engagement's off.

00:21:08.530 --> 00:21:10.530 line:80%
I don't know what to do.

00:21:10.530 --> 00:21:11.530 line:80%
Even with the engagement off,

00:21:12.290 --> 00:21:13.180 line:80%
you're still you.

00:21:13.890 --> 00:21:14.980 line:80%
You'll meet someone

00:21:14.980 --> 00:21:16.220 line:80%
who truly likes you someday.

00:21:19.130 --> 00:21:19.970 line:80%
Fengchi.

00:21:21.330 --> 00:21:22.180 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:24.180 --> 00:21:25.330 line:80%
Let me be alone.

00:21:54.890 --> 00:21:55.730 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:57.020 --> 00:21:58.780 line:80%
Xinrou's health hasn't recovered yet.

00:21:58.780 --> 00:21:59.700 line:80%
Why did she come over?

00:22:06.220 --> 00:22:07.060 line:80%
Have a seat.

00:22:12.290 --> 00:22:13.890 line:80%
Thank you for the medicine, Zhao.

00:22:14.420 --> 00:22:15.940 line:80%
I'm too weak.

00:22:15.940 --> 00:22:17.330 line:80%
I've made everyone worry.

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:23.890 line:80%
This softening powder

00:22:23.890 --> 00:22:24.730 line:80%
is truly potent.

00:22:25.090 --> 00:22:26.130 line:80%
You have no inner power.

00:22:26.130 --> 00:22:28.570 line:80%
So it should take ten to fifteen days

00:22:28.570 --> 00:22:29.570 line:80%
for you to recover.

00:22:32.890 --> 00:22:33.730 line:80%
Xinrou,

00:22:34.220 --> 00:22:35.610 line:80%
why can't you stop coughing?

00:22:41.290 --> 00:22:42.180 line:80%
Drink some water.

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:53.740 line:80%
If you knew you'd use softening powder,

00:22:54.420 --> 00:22:56.020 line:80%
you should've at least
told us beforehand.

00:22:57.020 --> 00:22:58.890 line:80%
Not everyone can endure that stuff.

00:23:00.330 --> 00:23:01.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:23:01.370 --> 00:23:02.460 line:80%
after tomorrow's memorial,

00:23:02.850 --> 00:23:04.530 line:80%
I'll send Xinrou back to Peiqiong Manor.

00:23:06.050 --> 00:23:07.420 line:80%
As for the wedding date...

00:23:10.460 --> 00:23:11.300 line:80%
What was that sound?

00:23:13.220 --> 00:23:15.090 line:80%
Most likely that stray cat again.

00:23:15.090 --> 00:23:16.130 line:80%
That stray cat again?

00:23:17.700 --> 00:23:19.370 line:80%
That stray cat is truly a nuisance.

00:23:19.370 --> 00:23:20.210 line:80%
I'll go have a look.

00:23:23.220 --> 00:23:24.700 line:80%
I'll go deal with that stray cat.

00:23:28.180 --> 00:23:29.660 line:80%
Zhao, you're so thoughtful.

00:23:30.610 --> 00:23:32.220 line:80%
She's a true heroine.

00:23:33.330 --> 00:23:34.370 line:80%
Unlike me,

00:23:35.290 --> 00:23:36.370 line:80%
so useless.

00:23:44.220 --> 00:23:45.370 line:80%
Why did you call me out here?

00:23:46.700 --> 00:23:47.780 line:80%
Spit it out.

00:23:48.530 --> 00:23:50.090 line:80%
If it's nothing important, I'm leaving.

00:23:50.810 --> 00:23:51.940 line:80%
The matter between us,

00:23:52.660 --> 00:23:54.020 line:80%
isn't that important too?

00:23:57.700 --> 00:23:59.180 line:80%
Come with me to find the Shi brothers.

00:23:59.660 --> 00:24:01.130 line:80%
Once we find the Shi brothers,

00:24:01.130 --> 00:24:02.890 line:80%
we might learn
where the Jade Sunflower is.

00:24:02.890 --> 00:24:03.730 line:80%
I'm not going.

00:24:05.500 --> 00:24:06.810 line:80%
The Man in Black is too important.

00:24:07.180 --> 00:24:08.420 line:80%
When I get back,

00:24:08.420 --> 00:24:10.290 line:80%
I'll report everything to Master.

00:24:10.570 --> 00:24:11.570 line:80%
What to do next

00:24:11.950 --> 00:24:13.420 line:80%
will be decided by Master and others.

00:24:13.810 --> 00:24:14.650 line:80%
Looks like

00:24:15.890 --> 00:24:17.740 line:80%
your Master doesn't tell you everything.

00:24:18.180 --> 00:24:19.780 line:80%
Don't you want to know

00:24:20.090 --> 00:24:21.460 line:80%
if Lu Chengnan was

00:24:21.460 --> 00:24:22.810 line:80%
your aunt's beloved?

00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:24.370 line:80%
Or...

00:24:25.330 --> 00:24:26.290 line:80%
the skin-painted demon?

00:24:26.940 --> 00:24:27.940 line:80%
How did you find out?

00:24:28.460 --> 00:24:30.420 line:80%
I've long suspected
your aunt loved another.

00:24:30.640 --> 00:24:32.890 line:80%
Otherwise, she wouldn't have let
Lord Zhou marry another.

00:24:34.050 --> 00:24:35.420 line:80%
If such a person truly exists,

00:24:35.890 --> 00:24:37.780 line:80%
with your aunt's upright nature,

00:24:38.220 --> 00:24:40.780 line:80%
she'd never let him hide till death.

00:24:41.420 --> 00:24:42.260 line:80%
Unless,

00:24:42.810 --> 00:24:43.980 line:80%
he's just like me,

00:24:45.180 --> 00:24:46.610 line:80%
a member of the Li Sect.

00:24:47.420 --> 00:24:48.460 line:80%
Why did your Master

00:24:48.460 --> 00:24:49.890 line:80%
call me

00:24:49.890 --> 00:24:51.460 line:80%
a skin-painted demon for no reason?

00:24:51.460 --> 00:24:53.500 line:80%
It must be because there was once

00:24:54.500 --> 00:24:56.020 line:80%
a skin-painted demon

00:24:56.780 --> 00:24:57.700 line:80%
from the Li Sect.

00:25:00.700 --> 00:25:01.780 line:80%
You're sharp.

00:25:02.700 --> 00:25:04.180 line:80%
My aunt did have a beloved.

00:25:05.420 --> 00:25:06.740 line:80%
But that person isn't Lu Chengnan.

00:25:08.180 --> 00:25:09.980 line:80%
Yet the couplet
found in the ancient tomb

00:25:09.980 --> 00:25:11.780 line:80%
was indeed written in her handwriting.

00:25:12.530 --> 00:25:13.660 line:80%
That couplet

00:25:14.140 --> 00:25:15.740 line:80%
doesn't read like
it was meant for a lover,

00:25:16.180 --> 00:25:17.460 line:80%
but rather for someone...

00:25:17.460 --> 00:25:18.370 line:80%
More like for a hero

00:25:18.810 --> 00:25:19.650 line:80%
she admired,

00:25:20.180 --> 00:25:21.020 line:80%
revered,

00:25:21.570 --> 00:25:23.130 line:80%
and respected.

00:25:26.180 --> 00:25:27.020 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:27.700 --> 00:25:28.850 line:80%
But if Lu Chengnan

00:25:29.530 --> 00:25:31.370 line:80%
wasn't the one your aunt loved,

00:25:32.420 --> 00:25:33.610 line:80%
then who

00:25:34.460 --> 00:25:37.220 line:80%
stole the Jade Sunflower
to heal the Shi brothers?

00:25:40.130 --> 00:25:41.130 line:80%
So

00:25:41.850 --> 00:25:43.050 line:80%
there's someone else

00:25:44.020 --> 00:25:46.050 line:80%
in the demon sect
guiding your aunt.

00:25:46.700 --> 00:25:47.660 line:80%
That person

00:25:48.020 --> 00:25:49.810 line:80%
is the true skin-painted demon.

00:25:51.180 --> 00:25:52.020 line:80%
Zhao.

00:25:52.610 --> 00:25:53.610 line:80%
Come with me

00:25:54.740 --> 00:25:56.130 line:80%
to find the Shi brothers.

00:25:56.810 --> 00:25:58.370 line:80%
Only they

00:25:58.890 --> 00:26:00.180 line:80%
hold the answers to all of this.

00:26:02.290 --> 00:26:04.570 line:80%
But the Shi brothers
have lived in seclusion for years,

00:26:04.570 --> 00:26:06.180 line:80%
how long will it take to find them?

00:26:06.700 --> 00:26:09.020 line:80%
Don't tell me you want me
to ditch the wedding.

00:26:11.020 --> 00:26:12.420 line:80%
Since you refuse to
call off the engagement,

00:26:13.330 --> 00:26:14.180 line:80%
what's wrong

00:26:14.850 --> 00:26:15.740 line:80%
with running?

00:26:16.050 --> 00:26:17.050 line:80%
I told you.

00:26:17.610 --> 00:26:19.330 line:80%
Luoying Valley keeps its word.

00:26:19.330 --> 00:26:21.420 line:80%
Breaking a promise
is absolutely unthinkable.

00:26:21.420 --> 00:26:23.420 line:80%
Besides, this marriage
was arranged by my aunt.

00:26:23.420 --> 00:26:24.370 line:80%
I can afford to lose face,

00:26:24.370 --> 00:26:25.290 line:80%
but she can't.

00:26:25.290 --> 00:26:26.220 line:80%
So what?

00:26:27.090 --> 00:26:27.930 line:80%
Forget it.

00:26:28.780 --> 00:26:30.370 line:80%
I won't trouble you, Mr. Mu.

00:26:30.370 --> 00:26:33.180 line:80%
If you still value our past friendship,

00:26:33.180 --> 00:26:34.570 line:80%
tell me if you find out

00:26:34.570 --> 00:26:35.500 line:80%
who it is later.

00:26:35.500 --> 00:26:36.980 line:80%
If not, it's fine.

00:26:36.980 --> 00:26:38.570 line:80%
I'll find out myself someday.

00:27:03.220 --> 00:27:05.500 line:80%
Aunt, these persimmon cakes
are delicious.

00:27:05.500 --> 00:27:07.180 line:80%
Let's buy more next time.

00:27:07.890 --> 00:27:09.460 line:80%
These delicious persimmon cakes

00:27:09.460 --> 00:27:11.330 line:80%
were sent by Aunt's good friends.

00:27:13.050 --> 00:27:14.700 line:80%
But whether we'll receive more

00:27:15.610 --> 00:27:16.740 line:80%
will depend on our luck.

00:27:17.460 --> 00:27:18.530 line:80%
Speaking of which,

00:27:19.420 --> 00:27:21.220 line:80%
it's been a long while
since I last saw them.

00:27:21.810 --> 00:27:23.460 line:80%
When I grow up,

00:27:23.460 --> 00:27:25.570 line:80%
I'll visit them on your behalf.

00:27:25.570 --> 00:27:26.890 line:80%
They've already retreated to

00:27:26.890 --> 00:27:28.780 line:80%
a place far, far away.

00:27:29.700 --> 00:27:31.420 line:80%
I fear you won't get to see them.

00:27:39.370 --> 00:27:41.180 line:80%
Elder Hu has been sent back
to the Li Sect.

00:27:41.180 --> 00:27:42.500 line:80%
With your order, Mr. Mu,

00:27:42.500 --> 00:27:43.700 line:80%
we can mobilize 100,000 sect members.

00:27:43.700 --> 00:27:44.850 line:80%
And Nie Zhe will surely be found.

00:27:49.290 --> 00:27:50.130 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:27:51.220 --> 00:27:52.060 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:27:55.180 --> 00:27:56.180 line:80%
Well, Shangguan,

00:27:56.850 --> 00:27:58.530 line:80%
can't you use your head?

00:27:58.890 --> 00:28:00.500 line:80%
Is now the time to talk about Nie Zhe?

00:28:01.050 --> 00:28:02.020 line:80%
If not capturing Nie Zhe,

00:28:02.020 --> 00:28:03.090 line:80%
what then?

00:28:03.090 --> 00:28:04.290 line:80%
If we don't think of a plan soon,

00:28:04.290 --> 00:28:05.570 line:80%
she'll be wed off.

00:28:09.020 --> 00:28:10.020 line:80%
Mr. Mu, rest assured,

00:28:10.020 --> 00:28:11.220 line:80%
I'll make sure

00:28:11.220 --> 00:28:13.700 line:80%
Miss Cai's wedding falls through.

00:28:20.500 --> 00:28:22.420 line:80%
Since Luoying Valley
can't break their promise,

00:28:25.180 --> 00:28:26.700 line:80%
what about Peiqiong Manor?

00:28:30.080 --> 00:28:31.090 line:80%
Mr. Mu, please take a look.

00:28:31.610 --> 00:28:33.700 line:80%
This is the most beautiful courtesan
in Wu'an Town.

00:28:34.090 --> 00:28:36.220 line:80%
I'll hire her with heavy gold

00:28:36.220 --> 00:28:38.220 line:80%
to set a trap for Zhou Yuqi.

00:28:38.610 --> 00:28:39.610 line:80%
You call this beauty?

00:28:40.420 --> 00:28:42.130 line:80%
She's not even one-tenth
as pretty as Zhao.

00:28:42.570 --> 00:28:44.220 line:80%
If Zhou Yuqi isn't blind,

00:28:44.220 --> 00:28:45.500 line:80%
how could he leave Zhao for her?

00:28:45.890 --> 00:28:47.130 line:80%
You're right, Mr. Mu.

00:28:47.740 --> 00:28:51.020 line:80%
Miss Cai is a rare beauty.

00:28:51.020 --> 00:28:52.130 line:80%
Of course, no one compares to her.

00:28:52.570 --> 00:28:53.570 line:80%
But

00:28:53.570 --> 00:28:55.780 line:80%
with my Seduction Powder,

00:28:55.780 --> 00:28:57.460 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi will definitely submit.

00:28:57.460 --> 00:28:59.570 line:80%
Mr. Mu, don't heed
Master You's foolish idea.

00:28:59.570 --> 00:29:01.420 line:80%
If we drug him into losing his chastity,

00:29:01.420 --> 00:29:02.700 line:80%
with Miss Cai's personality,

00:29:02.700 --> 00:29:03.940 line:80%
she won't be angry.

00:29:03.940 --> 00:29:05.290 line:80%
Instead, she'll think

00:29:05.290 --> 00:29:06.570 line:80%
he's framed

00:29:06.570 --> 00:29:08.290 line:80%
and pity him.

00:29:08.290 --> 00:29:10.180 line:80%
It's a terrible plan,
not worth it at all.

00:29:10.180 --> 00:29:11.850 line:80%
You have a better plan?

00:29:11.850 --> 00:29:12.690 line:80%
Go on, let's hear it.

00:29:13.050 --> 00:29:14.530 line:80%
Cut the mess clean and quick.

00:29:15.290 --> 00:29:16.130 line:80%
Handle it directly.

00:29:18.850 --> 00:29:20.460 line:80%
So that's your brilliant idea?

00:29:20.460 --> 00:29:21.530 line:80%
If Miss Cai found out,

00:29:21.530 --> 00:29:23.090 line:80%
she'll stab Mr. Mu right away.

00:29:23.090 --> 00:29:24.330 line:80%
You call my idea terrible?

00:29:24.330 --> 00:29:26.220 line:80%
Yours is worse than swill!

00:29:26.220 --> 00:29:27.180 line:80%
Alright.

00:29:28.740 --> 00:29:29.850 line:80%
For marriage,

00:29:34.660 --> 00:29:36.090 line:80%
winning the heart comes first.

00:29:43.810 --> 00:29:45.420 line:80%
Pack up after the ceremony.

00:29:45.420 --> 00:29:46.780 line:80%
Leave for Qingque Sect tomorrow morning.

00:29:51.090 --> 00:29:51.930 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:29:52.850 --> 00:29:53.980 line:80%
Shangguan Haonan.

00:29:54.460 --> 00:29:56.530 line:80%
The Young Master
asks to talk to you in the side room.

00:29:56.530 --> 00:29:57.530 line:80%
Nothing to talk about.

00:29:58.600 --> 00:30:00.500 line:80%
The Young Master
mentioned the persimmon cakes...

00:30:04.460 --> 00:30:05.330 line:80%
Then I'll go talk.

00:30:05.330 --> 00:30:06.220 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:30:07.290 --> 00:30:08.130 line:80%
Mr. Song.

00:30:09.460 --> 00:30:11.290 line:80%
The Young Master only invited Miss Cai.

00:30:11.290 --> 00:30:12.290 line:80%
I must go.

00:30:12.290 --> 00:30:13.500 line:80%
Then I'll have to intrude as well.

00:30:15.090 --> 00:30:16.180 line:80%
It's all right, Yuzhi.

00:30:16.180 --> 00:30:17.850 line:80%
I can go alone.

00:30:17.850 --> 00:30:18.690 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:30:38.890 --> 00:30:39.730 line:80%
Yeah.

00:30:39.980 --> 00:30:42.460 line:80%
I hid the persimmon cakes from the tomb.

00:30:42.460 --> 00:30:43.610 line:80%
Because I thought...

00:30:43.610 --> 00:30:45.500 line:80%
You thought that persimmon cake
with six corners

00:30:46.050 --> 00:30:46.940 line:80%
was extremely rare.

00:30:47.530 --> 00:30:48.370 line:80%
Just now,

00:30:49.420 --> 00:30:50.500 line:80%
why didn't you come over?

00:31:03.940 --> 00:31:05.370 line:80%
Right and wrong must be kept apart.

00:31:05.370 --> 00:31:07.610 line:80%
Besides, I'm already engaged.

00:31:07.610 --> 00:31:08.780 line:80%
Of course, I should avoid suspicion.

00:31:09.370 --> 00:31:10.610 line:80%
You're about to leave.

00:31:11.460 --> 00:31:12.780 line:80%
Shouldn't you

00:31:12.780 --> 00:31:13.980 line:80%
come and say goodbye to me?

00:31:23.220 --> 00:31:24.850 line:80%
Not even a farewell drink?

00:31:25.290 --> 00:31:26.570 line:80%
You came just to say farewell?

00:31:26.570 --> 00:31:27.570 line:80%
Absolutely not.

00:31:28.890 --> 00:31:29.730 line:80%
I said

00:31:30.050 --> 00:31:31.610 line:80%
I'd pester you forever.

00:31:32.180 --> 00:31:33.420 line:80%
Never let go.

00:31:39.050 --> 00:31:40.330 line:80%
You want to marry someone else?

00:31:43.050 --> 00:31:44.500 line:80%
Over my dead body.

00:31:45.740 --> 00:31:46.740 line:80%
Madman.

00:32:20.610 --> 00:32:21.780 line:80%
Wu'an Town has nice mountain goods.

00:32:22.180 --> 00:32:23.090 line:80%
Buy some

00:32:23.090 --> 00:32:24.090 line:80%
to take back tomorrow.

00:32:26.220 --> 00:32:27.330 line:80%
Let's go check over there.

00:32:28.220 --> 00:32:29.060 line:80%
Go!

00:32:31.570 --> 00:32:32.780 line:80%
You shameless woman.

00:32:33.460 --> 00:32:35.660 line:80%
You've been married to me
for over ten years.

00:32:35.660 --> 00:32:37.890 line:80%
Yet you still pine for that man?

00:32:37.890 --> 00:32:40.660 line:80%
Since your heart
still holds that Yuan guy,

00:32:41.050 --> 00:32:43.660 line:80%
why did you marry me in the first place?

00:32:44.570 --> 00:32:46.980 line:80%
You let me live for all these years as

00:32:46.980 --> 00:32:48.660 line:80%
a man deceived and mocked!

00:32:51.050 --> 00:32:52.090 line:80%
Look at this for yourself.

00:32:52.850 --> 00:32:54.890 line:80%
What nonsense have you written here?

00:32:56.460 --> 00:32:58.740 line:80%
(Cousin)
I'm going to settle this with him now!

00:32:59.180 --> 00:33:01.290 line:80%
Don't! I do like him,

00:33:02.020 --> 00:33:03.530 line:80%
but I married you

00:33:03.530 --> 00:33:05.980 line:80%
because of my parents' orders.

00:33:06.460 --> 00:33:08.180 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:33:08.180 --> 00:33:09.810 line:80%
I'll endure your blows and scolding.

00:33:09.810 --> 00:33:10.650 line:80%
Get out!

00:33:11.460 --> 00:33:12.500 line:80%
Get the hell out!

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:14.810 line:80%
Pei Zhisong.

00:33:14.810 --> 00:33:16.500 line:80%
You heartless man!

00:33:18.980 --> 00:33:20.570 line:80%
You sneaking seducer.

00:33:20.980 --> 00:33:22.180 line:80%
You lecherous scumbag!

00:33:23.370 --> 00:33:24.810 line:80%
Adulterers!

00:33:25.090 --> 00:33:25.930 line:80%
Such disgrace.

00:33:26.220 --> 00:33:27.370 line:80%
This is immoral.

00:33:27.370 --> 00:33:28.290 line:80%
It is against all decorum.

00:33:31.370 --> 00:33:32.700 line:80%
Back then, I was too timid.

00:33:33.290 --> 00:33:34.500 line:80%
I didn't break off the engagement.

00:33:35.180 --> 00:33:37.020 line:80%
And made you suffer so greatly.

00:33:38.050 --> 00:33:39.220 line:80%
If I'd known this would happen,

00:33:39.890 --> 00:33:41.700 line:80%
I never would've done it!

00:33:42.370 --> 00:33:43.570 line:80%
How embarrassing!

00:33:47.850 --> 00:33:48.690 line:80%
Xinrou!

00:33:49.610 --> 00:33:50.450 line:80%
Xinrou!

00:33:50.940 --> 00:33:52.290 line:80%
How can she be so unchaste?

00:33:56.980 --> 00:33:57.820 line:80%
Xinrou!

00:33:58.700 --> 00:33:59.540 line:80%
Yuqi.

00:33:59.980 --> 00:34:01.370 line:80%
Xinrou, don't worry.

00:34:01.370 --> 00:34:03.740 line:80%
I will have Mother
find you a good marriage.

00:34:03.740 --> 00:34:04.580 line:80%
I will not marry!

00:34:05.500 --> 00:34:06.530 line:80%
I will marry no one.

00:34:07.370 --> 00:34:08.930 line:80%
I only ask that you don't drive me away.

00:34:09.410 --> 00:34:10.250 line:80%
I know.

00:34:10.850 --> 00:34:12.450 line:80%
After you marry Miss Cai,

00:34:12.830 --> 00:34:14.220 line:80%
the Zhou clan won't have a place for me.

00:34:15.490 --> 00:34:16.780 line:80%
When that day comes,

00:34:16.780 --> 00:34:17.930 line:80%
I'll become a nun!

00:34:17.930 --> 00:34:19.010 line:80%
How could there not be?

00:34:22.010 --> 00:34:23.140 line:80%
As long as you're willing,

00:34:24.220 --> 00:34:26.540 line:80%
the Zhou clan will always
have a spot for you.

00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:28.380 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:34:29.370 --> 00:34:30.210 line:80%
by then,

00:34:31.220 --> 00:34:32.810 line:80%
you'll be powerless too.

00:34:33.740 --> 00:34:35.060 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:34:35.740 --> 00:34:37.780 line:80%
I'd rather live
a Life of Monastic Devotion,

00:34:38.180 --> 00:34:39.410 line:80%
and for you and Miss Cai,

00:34:39.810 --> 00:34:40.970 line:80%
pray for blessings all my life.

00:34:41.540 --> 00:34:42.380 line:80%
Xinrou.

00:34:42.540 --> 00:34:43.410 line:80%
Yuqi.

00:34:52.100 --> 00:34:53.220 line:80%
Falling petals yearn.

00:34:53.970 --> 00:34:55.410 line:80%
But the stream flows on.

00:34:55.810 --> 00:34:57.450 line:80%
Yuqi, please stop trying to persuade me.

00:34:58.540 --> 00:34:59.890 line:80%
My heart is as calm as still water.

00:35:11.220 --> 00:35:12.060 line:80%
Xinrou.

00:35:16.850 --> 00:35:17.690 line:80%
Xinrou!

00:35:21.330 --> 00:35:22.170 line:80%
Ding.

00:35:22.540 --> 00:35:23.380 line:80%
Fan.

00:35:30.490 --> 00:35:31.370 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou.

00:35:32.340 --> 00:35:33.660 line:80%
I've been talking to you all this time.

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:34.850 line:80%
Just to make one thing clear.

00:35:35.330 --> 00:35:36.810 line:80%
Since ancient times,

00:35:36.810 --> 00:35:38.410 line:80%
those who want it all,

00:35:38.810 --> 00:35:40.010 line:80%
who play both sides

00:35:40.490 --> 00:35:41.700 line:80%
never end well.

00:35:42.410 --> 00:35:43.890 line:80%
Miss Min has no title,

00:35:43.890 --> 00:35:45.580 line:80%
yet staying at the Zhou clan.

00:35:45.580 --> 00:35:47.810 line:80%
It's really inappropriate,
don't you think?

00:35:47.810 --> 00:35:48.720 line:80%
No way.

00:35:48.730 --> 00:35:49.780 line:80%
I can't abandon Xinrou.

00:35:50.410 --> 00:35:51.890 line:80%
Why can't you understand?

00:35:51.890 --> 00:35:53.060 line:80%
Why won't you listen?

00:35:55.740 --> 00:35:56.620 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou.

00:35:57.100 --> 00:35:58.810 line:80%
Let me speak plainly
before anything else.

00:35:58.810 --> 00:36:01.010 line:80%
Zhao belongs to all of us.

00:36:01.010 --> 00:36:03.490 line:80%
If she suffers any grievance
after marriage,

00:36:03.490 --> 00:36:04.930 line:80%
or if someone dares to mistreat her,

00:36:05.780 --> 00:36:07.970 line:80%
we'll have no choice but to fight.

00:36:10.780 --> 00:36:11.620 line:80%
Let's go.

00:36:42.340 --> 00:36:47.700 line:80%
(Fortune-telling)

00:36:52.010 --> 00:36:52.850 line:80%
Young Master.

00:36:54.700 --> 00:36:55.540 line:80%
Young Master.

00:36:59.580 --> 00:37:00.660 line:80%
Young Master, please wait.

00:37:01.490 --> 00:37:02.660 line:80%
Sir, what is it?

00:37:03.740 --> 00:37:04.850 line:80%
Looking at your face,

00:37:04.850 --> 00:37:06.140 line:80%
your love line's dim,

00:37:06.140 --> 00:37:07.930 line:80%
so relationships might be rough.

00:37:07.930 --> 00:37:09.780 line:80%
And your forehead is dark,

00:37:09.780 --> 00:37:11.370 line:80%
which points to pent-up worries.

00:37:11.370 --> 00:37:12.250 line:80%
Why not

00:37:12.250 --> 00:37:13.410 line:80%
tell me about it?

00:37:13.410 --> 00:37:15.700 line:80%
I can help untangle your worries.

00:37:23.620 --> 00:37:24.460 line:80%
Young Master Zhou.

00:37:25.930 --> 00:37:27.140 line:80%
How did you know...

00:37:40.641 --> 00:37:51.301 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:38:10.061 --> 00:38:14.471 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:38:15.036 --> 00:38:19.651 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:38:19.991 --> 00:38:24.556 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:38:25.081 --> 00:38:29.381 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:38:32.326 --> 00:38:37.026 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:37.551 --> 00:38:41.841 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:42.501 --> 00:38:46.531 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:46.846 --> 00:38:51.971 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:52.546 --> 00:38:57.356 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:57.571 --> 00:39:01.741 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:02.466 --> 00:39:06.401 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:06.901 --> 00:39:12.176 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:39:34.906 --> 00:39:40.036 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:40.401 --> 00:39:44.771 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:45.036 --> 00:39:49.166 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:49.351 --> 00:39:54.926 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪